y seat insert<o:p></o:p></li><li class="MsoNormal">Adjustable headrest<o:p></o:p></li><li class="MsoNormal">Integrated ISOFIX base with support leg<o:p></o:p></li><li class="MsoNormal">Helpful ISOFIX installation indicators<o:p></o:p></li></ul></div></div><div data-label="Button" data-key="button" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1682331436682" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-gpicon-button" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1682331436682"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-stretch-lg="0"><a class="button btn gf_button gf_gs-button-element gf_gs-button---large" href="https://icklebubba.com/collections/car-seats/products/radius-360-rotating-car-seat#" target="" data-scroll-speed="2000" data-exc=""><span>Buy now</span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1717598781968" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1717598781968"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1682331160420" data-id="1682331160420"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1717598781931" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1717598781931"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-3">Radial i-Size 360 Spin 40-150cm car seat</h2></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1717598781943" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1717598781943" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>The <a href="https://icklebubba.com/collections/baby-to-junior-car-seats/products/radial-i-size-plus-360-spin-40-150cm-car-seat" class="">Ickle Bubba Radial i-Size Plus car seat</a> offers a 360-degree rotating function, so you can place baby in and out of the car seat with ease, along with providing extra protection and peace of mind through the ECE R129 safety standard (i-Size).&nbsp;</p></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1717598781955" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1717598781955" data-layout-lg="6+6" data-extraclass="" data-layout-md="6+6" data-layout-sm="6+6" data-layout-xs="12+12"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1682331192275" data-id="1682331192275"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1717598781983" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1717598781983"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en"><p>Built to last, the i-Size Radial is suitable for use from birth all the way up to 150cm (approx. 12 years*). The i-Size standard means baby can be in a safer, rear-facing position up to 105cm (approx. 4 years*), providing enhanced protection, and the forward-facing position can be used from 100cm to 150cm (approx. 15 months - 12 years*).</p><p><br></p><p>Features:</p><p><br></p><p>•	Size compliant</p><p><br></p><p>•	Rotating 360-degree seat</p><p><br></p><p>•	Easy one-handed headrest and harness adjustment</p><p><br></p><p>•	Integrated ISOFIX base</p><p><br></p><p>•	Stabilising support leg</p><p><br></p><p>•	Cosy infant seat insert</p><p><br></p><p>•	Chest and crotch buckle pads</p><p><br></p><p>•	Rear-facing seat recline</p><p><br></p><p>•	Removable fabric cover and harness</p><p><br></p><p></p></div></div></div><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1682331193347" data-id="1682331193347"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1717598781879" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1717598781879" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center g